Day 2 - Nov 29

to access using secure crt
- click kidlat
- protocol --> serial
- port --> com3 usb-serial ch340
- uncheck --> XON/OFF
- click connect

========================================================
to access vmware windows server 2022 - ctrl+alt+insert

=======================================================
To create new DNS ZONE
go to powershell ISE
go to createDNSZONES.ps1
edit existing syntax (For example bpi.ph.com to gcash.ph.com -- control H then replace all)
once done click run

=============================================================
To verify Newly created DNS Zone
go to server manager
click --> tools
click --> DNS
click --> NAS
click --> forward lookup zones
*newly created DNS zone should be visible under forward lookup zones

==============================================================
create new Host (A or AAAA) for gcash.ph.com (without www)
leave Name blank
add ip add 10.31.1.8

===========================================================
create Mail exchange
right click on gcash.ph.com
click new Mail Exchanger (MX)
leave blank on Host or child domain
FQDN -> gcash.ph.com
click ok
*for connectivity ping the ip 10.31.1.8 (this ip is in rivan room only)

================================================================
Create gcash website
go to powershell -->  create website tab
replace path with new url from gcash
("C:\DNS-CONFIG-main\DNS-CONFIG-main\bank-phishing-sites\gcash"
click run (make sure no error)

================================================================
to create mail server
click hMailServer Administrator
default password C1sc0123
check first if autoban is disabled

=================================================================
to create domain
click domains
- click add (gcash.ph.com)

====================================================================
to create email accounts
click domain
click account
click add (*@gcash.ph.com)

=================================================================
to setup email account in thunderbird
click new acount --> email
input full name and email address (based from account created in hMail)
click manual configuration
*for incoming server select IMAP
hostname imap.gcash.ph.com
make sure port is 143 for IMAP
click next
*for outgoing server select IMAP
hostname imap.gcash.ph.com
click test (font should be color green for successful testing)
click continue

