---------------
how to deploy new agent
select window
input server ip 
create agent name
select default
copy command to windows powershell (dos)
copy command start agent 

How to debug if normal adding of agent did not work
go to drive c--> program file (x86) --> ossec-agent --> click win32ui.exe --> click view --> click config
--> copy config to notepad++
edit server IP
saved and copy paste to ossec notepad. Click manage --> click stop --> click start ---> then refresh wazuh in browser to verify if agent is added

---------------------
For File Integrity monitoring
sample only: create a folder in desktop --> add any text file as sample
Go to win32ui.exe --> view config --> copy and paste config to notepad++ 
go to line 91 and add this directory:
<directories realtime="yes" report_changes="yes" check_all="yes">C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\Rivan31</directories> 
copy paste config to ossec notepad then save
Go to file integrity monitoring --> click inventory --> click 
